name: Endurance w/Sprints into Zone 3 #2
description:
High intensity work is a little easier when fresh. In today's workout the aim is to produce high intensity when fatigued. We build fatigue through endurance riding, before completing a range of sprint efforts, leading a 5min Zone 3 effort.
